metadata.title: Mark Recovery Program Multiple Finclip Database (Canada)
metadata.description:
Parameter Biological data from the salmonid finclip database Biological samples are collected to determine age-class structure, age/size interrelationships, hatchery evaluations and growth rates.
Geographic Area coastal British Columbia

Publication
CDFO technical reports

[ A TCODE project ]
